.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-3::.
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, cauliflower, grapes, lettuce
There are 4 different nationalities: american, british, chinese, french
4 different pets are kept: fish, frog, mouse, rabbit
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, snowboarding, tennis, weightlifting
House: colonial, cottage, townhouse, wooden
 1. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the townhouse house##1
 3. the person eating grapes is the owner of the rabbit##1
 4. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the wooden house##1
 5. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
 6. the wooden house is the person eating grapes##1
 7. the chinese is on the left of the wooden house##1
 8. the colonial house is on the right of the townhouse house##1
 9. the french is the owner of the frog##1
10. the british is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
11. the wooden house is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
12. the person eating grapes is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3    |       4       |
| Food          | cabbage    | lettuce      | grapes  | cauliflower   |
| Nationality   | french     | chinese      | british | american      |
| Pet           | frog       | fish         | rabbit  | mouse         |
| Sport         | basketball | snowboarding | tennis  | weightlifting |
| House     | townhouse       | colonial         | wooden   | cottage        |

