.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-18::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, rowing, badminton, water-polo
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, magic-tricks, video-games, woodworking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, mystery, thriller, western
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, british, indonesian, mexican
4 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, rat, snake
 1. the indonesian is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's sport is rowing is the person watching western movies##1
 3. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
 4. the mexican is on the left of the brazilian##1
 5. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person who's sport is badminton##1
 6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
 8. the brazilian is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
 9. the owner of the chinchilla is the person watching thriller movies##1
10. the person watching thriller movies is on the far left##1
11. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
12. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |      3       |    4     |
| Sport      | water-polo       | badminton      | rowing      | cycling    |
| Hobby         | woodworking | video-games | magic-tricks | dancing  |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller    | mystery     | western      | disaster |
| Nationality   | indonesian  | mexican     | brazilian    | british  |
| Pet           | chinchilla  | snake       | cat          | rat      |

