.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-19::.
There 4 different types of food: lime, plum, raspberry, tomato
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, rock-climbing, singing, video-games
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, horror, mystery, western
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, parkour, rowing, skiing
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, juice, 7up, milk
 1. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far left##1
 2. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
 3. the person drinking 7up is the person who's hobby is singing##1
 4. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
 5. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
 6. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 7. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person eating lime##1
 8. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person eating lime##1
 9. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person eating plum##1
10. the person who's sport is skiing is the person eating raspberry##1
11. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
12. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far right##1
13. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |      3      |       4       |
| Food          | tomato      | plum     | lime        | raspberry     |
| Hobby         | singing     | chess    | video-games | rock-climbing |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | mystery  | horror      | western       |
| Sport         | rowing      | lacrosse | parkour     | skiing        |
| Beverage     | 7up   | milk     | almond-milk  | juice       |

